{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-9","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor početlja i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">f</span> je zvuk koji proizvode tvoje usne i zubi. Da bi izgovorio <span class=\"highlighted-text\">f</span>, nežno stavite gornje zube uz donju usnu i pustite vazduh da lako prođe između njih.</p>\n<p>Za razliku od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span> na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span> gde vam usne savršeno dodiruju, za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">f</span> vaše usne se potpuno zatvaraju kada izgovorite ovaj blagi zvuk, koji je ponovljen polaganim curenjem vazduha kroz mali prostor između zuba i donje usne.</p>\n<p>Ponekad možete čuti ovaj početak izgovoren kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fo</span>. Ovo je zato što dodavanje jednostavnog nastavka od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span> čini ovaj početak zvučnijim.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">f</span> prati završetak <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dobija slogove: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fa</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fo</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fu</span>.</p>\n<p>Kao što je slučaj sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span>, prilikom izgovaranja ovih slogova, lako spojite zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">f</span> direktno i bez prekida sa završetkom između njih. Jedina razlika će biti oblik usta koje pravite za svaki specifičan završetak.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">f</span> na ovim slogovima, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fu</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Karakter</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fū</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">夫</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fú</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">芙</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fǔ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">抚</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">fù</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">父</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-9"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Wang Hua","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_initials.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":172.3,"finishTimestamp":190.31},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.89,"dialogue":{"text":"f","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.6,"finishTime":6.38,"dialogue":{"text":"fa","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.17,"finishTime":8.05,"dialogue":{"text":"fo","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.22,"finishTime":10.08,"dialogue":{"text":"fu","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":11.72,"finishTime":12.55,"dialogue":{"text":"fū","align":"center"}},{